      <title>绿色电力产量激增，欧洲电价转为负值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/european-power-prices-turn-negative-as-green-power-output-jumps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于风能和太阳能发电量将大幅增长，并为电网提供大量绿色电力，周三欧洲几个市场的电价跌至零以下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/european-power-prices-turn-negative-as-green-power-output-jumps</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2024 13:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
